<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>KYC Verification Update - Cowors</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .title.approved {
            color: #059669;
        }
        .title.rejected {
            color: #dc2626;
        }
        .title.pending {
            color: #d97706;
        }
        .title.required {
            color: #7c3aed;
        }
        .status-box {
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border-left: 4px solid;
        }
        .status-box.approved {
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            border-left-color: #059669;
        }
        .status-box.rejected {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border-left-color: #dc2626;
        }
        .status-box.pending {
            background-color: #fffbeb;
            border-left-color: #d97706;
        }
        .status-box.required {
            background-color: #faf5ff;
            border-left-color: #7c3aed;
        }
        .status-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .status-icon.approved {
            color: #059669;
        }
        .status-icon.rejected {
            color: #dc2626;
        }
        .status-icon.pending {
            color: #d97706;
        }
        .status-icon.required {
            color: #7c3aed;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #1d4ed8;
        }
        .cta-button.success {
            background-color: #059669;
        }
        .cta-button.success:hover {
            background-color: #047857;
        }
        .cta-button.warning {
            background-color: #d97706;
        }
        .cta-button.warning:hover {
            background-color: #b45309;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #2563eb;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .document-list {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .document-list ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Cowors</div>
            {{#if (eq status 'approved')}}
                <div class="status-icon approved">‚úÖ</div>
                <h1 class="title approved">KYC Verification Approved!</h1>
            {{else if (eq status 'rejected')}}
                <div class="status-icon rejected">‚ùå</div>
                <h1 class="title rejected">KYC Verification Rejected</h1>
            {{else if (eq status 'pending')}}
                <div class="status-icon pending">‚è≥</div>
                <h1 class="title pending">KYC Verification Under Review</h1>
            {{else}}
                <div class="status-icon required">üìã</div>
                <h1 class="title required">KYC Verification Required</h1>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <span class="highlight">{{firstName}}</span>,</p>
            
            {{#if (eq status 'approved')}}
                <div class="status-box approved">
                    <p><strong>Congratulations!</strong> Your identity verification has been successfully completed and approved.</p>
                    <p>You now have full access to all Cowors features, including:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>‚úÖ Book premium workspaces</li>
                        <li>‚úÖ Access exclusive member benefits</li>
                        <li>‚úÖ Higher booking limits</li>
                        <li>‚úÖ Priority customer support</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="cta-button success">Explore Premium Spaces</a>
                </div>
                
            {{else if (eq status 'rejected')}}
                <div class="status-box rejected">
                    <p><strong>We're sorry,</strong> but we were unable to verify your identity with the documents provided.</p>
                    
                    {{#if rejectionReason}}
                    <p><strong>Reason for rejection:</strong></p>
                    <p>{{rejectionReason}}</p>
                    {{/if}}
                    
                    <p>Don't worry! You can resubmit your verification documents. Please ensure:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>üì∑ Documents are clear and readable</li>
                        <li>üìÑ All information is visible</li>
                        <li>‚úÖ Documents are valid and not expired</li>
                        <li>üÜî Name matches your account information</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="cta-button warning">Resubmit Documents</a>
                </div>
                
            {{else if (eq status 'pending')}}
                <div class="status-box pending">
                    <p><strong>Thank you for submitting your verification documents!</strong></p>
                    <p>Our team is currently reviewing your submission. This process typically takes 1-3 business days.</p>
                    <p>We'll notify you as soon as the review is complete.</p>
                    
                    <p><strong>What happens next:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>üîç Our team reviews your documents</li>
                        <li>üìß You'll receive an email with the results</li>
                        <li>‚úÖ Upon approval, you'll gain access to premium features</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
            {{else}}
                <div class="status-box required">
                    <p><strong>To unlock all Cowors features,</strong> we need to verify your identity.</p>
                    <p>This is a quick and secure process that helps us maintain a safe community for all our members.</p>
                    
                    {{#if documentsRequired}}
                    <div class="document-list">
                        <p><strong>Required documents:</strong></p>
                        <ul>
                            {{#each documentsRequired}}
                            <li>{{this}}</li>
                            {{/each}}
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    
                    <p><strong>Benefits of verification:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>üè¢ Access to premium workspaces</li>
                        <li>üíº Higher booking limits</li>
                        <li>üéØ Exclusive member perks</li>
                        <li>üõ°Ô∏è Enhanced account security</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="cta-button">Start Verification</a>
                </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <p>If you have any questions about the verification process, our support team is here to help.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                <a href="{{supportUrl}}" style="color: #6b7280; text-decoration: none;">Contact Support</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>Thank you for being part of the Cowors community!</p>
            
            <p><strong>The Cowors Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>KYC verification update sent to {{firstName}}</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Cowors. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>